Mix vinegar, oil, sugar and seasoning. Pour over potatoes in bowl; stir to coat. Refrigerate at least 1 hour. Can be overnight. Before serving, cut lettuce in half. Rinse; drain well. Place one half on plate, cut side down. Cut remaining lettuce into 1 inch chunks. Thread potatoes, lettuce chunks and sausage alternately onto skewers. Drizzle with dressing remaining in bowl. Insert skewers into lettuce half.